It should be noted that the shell of fig. 1 (
Schütt, 2004
) is the same shell as the one depicted on fig. 7 (
Schütt, 1996
), but the legend differs: “Ispir, Stadtge- biet” (SMF 318769a) versus “Çoruh-Fluß, etwa 10 km N Ispir, Böschung unterhalb Köç” (SMF 318769b), respectively. The legend of 2004 is in fact the same as the label of fig. 6 of the 1996 paper, but this is a different shell.
